s Criteria (Revised - More Demanding)\\n\\nA system is successful when it can:\\n1. Take any new turn-based game (via a standardized interface)\\n2. Reach >95% predictive accuracy on legal moves within a reasonable number of games\\n3. Produce a human-readable + machine-executable formal rule set\\n4. Generalize across game categories (board, card, abstract strategy, stochastic, imperfect info)\\n5. Demonstrate emergent discovery of concepts like \\\"check\\\", \\\"castling rights\\\", \\\"mana\\\", \\\"phases\\\", \\\"win conditions\\\" without ever being told they exist.\\n\\nThis SPEC.md is a living document. It will be rewritten as better insights emerge.\\n\\n**Current directive to self:** Critique this aggressively. Improve or replace the architecture with something more principled. Prioritize mathematical elegance and real capability over fidelity to the initial description.\\nEOF\"}"}}], "tool_name": null, "timestamp": 1781147628.783089, "token_count": null, "finish_reason": "tool_calls", "reasoning": null, "reasoning_content": null, "reasoning_details": null, "codex_reasoning_items": null, "codex_message_items": null, "platform_message_id": null, "observed": 0, "active": 1}, {"id": 621, "session_id": "20260610_231007_a87616c6", "role": "tool", "content": "{\"output\": \"\", \"exit_code\": 0, \"error\": null}", "tool_call_id": "call-eb5917b0-bf7a-4bd3-bbac-6a30e1355165-10", "tool_calls": null, "tool_name": "terminal", "timestamp": 1781147628.789975, "token_count": null, "finish_reason": null, "reasoning": null, "reasoning_content": null, "reasoning_details": null, "codex_reasoning_items": null, "codex_message_items": null, "platform_message_id": null, "observed": 0, "active": 1}, {"id": 622, "session_id": "20260610_231007_a87616c6", "role": "assistant", "content": "", "tool_call_id": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call-fc312e50-f09b-4309-a67f-ee77ebe17593-11", "call_id": "call-fc312e50-f09b-4309-a67f-ee77ebe17593-11", "response_item_id": "fc_816cfdd7-c9f6-93a4